         <lb n="c58-0033__main__1"/> he or I shall perish in mortal conflict. For this <lb n="c58-0033__main__2"/> purpose I will preserve my life: to ex<del rend="strikethrough" sID="c58-0033__main__d6e2649"/>c<del eID="c58-0033__main__d6e2649"/>e<mod sID="c58-0033__main__d6e2652"/>
