               <metamark xmlns:mith="http://mith.umd.edu/sc/ns1#" function="insert">^</metamark>
            <add eID="c58-0033__main__d6e2698"/>
            <add place="superlinear" sID="c58-0033__main__d6e2704"/>the furies<add eID="c58-0033__main__d6e2704"/>
         <mod eID="c58-0033__main__d6e2693"/> possessed me as I concluded, and rage choaked <lb n="c58-0033__main__15"/> my utterance. <add hand="#comp" place="intralinear" sID="c58-0033__main__d6e2710"/>
            <metamark xmlns:mith="http://mith.umd.edu/sc/ns1#" function="paragraph">
          [</metamark>
         <add eID="c58-0033__main__d6e2710"/>I was answered through the stillness <lb n="c58-0033__main__16"/> of night by a <del rend="strikethrough" sID="c58-0033__main__d6e2718"/>lon<del eID="c58-0033__main__d6e2718"/> loud and fiendish laugh. It rung <lb n="c58-0033__main__17"/> on my ears long and heavily; the mountains re-echoed <lb n="c58-0033__main__18"/> it and I felt as if all hell surrounded me with mock <lb n="c58-0033__main__19"/> ery and laughter. Surely in that moment I should<zone eID="c58-0033__main"/>
