      <zone type="main" sID="c58-0034__main"/> 
         <lb n="c58-0034__main__1"/> have been possessed by frenzy and have destroyed my <lb n="c58-0034__main__2"/> miserable existence, but that my vow was heard <lb n="c58-0034__main__3"/> and I was reserved for vengeance. The laughter died <lb n="c58-0034__main__4"/> away when a well known and abhorred voice <w xmlns:mith="http://mith.umd.edu/sc/ns1#" ana="start"/>ap<lb n="c58-0034__main__5"/>parently<w xmlns:mith="http://mith.umd.edu/sc/ns1#" ana="end"/> close to my ear, addressed me in an audible <lb n="c58-0034__main__6"/> whisper; "I am satisfied; <del rend="strikethrough" sID="c58-0034__main__d6e2753"/>yo<del eID="c58-0034__main__d6e2753"/> miserable wretch, you <lb n="c58-0034__main__7"/> have determined to live and I am satisfied."<milestone xmlns:mith="http://mith.umd.edu/sc/ns1#" unit="tei:p"/> 
         <lb n="c58-0034__main__8"/> I darted towards the spot from which the <lb n="c58-0034__main__9"/> sound proceeded but the devil eluded my grasp; <w xmlns:mith="http://mith.umd.edu/sc/ns1#" ana="start"/>sud<lb n="c58-0034__main__10"/>denly<w xmlns:mith="http://mith.umd.edu/sc/ns1#" ana="end"/> the broard disk of the moon arose and shone <lb n="c58-0034__main__11"/> full<del rend="strikethrough" sID="c58-0034__main__d6e2774"/>y<del eID="c58-0034__main__d6e2774"/> upon his ghastly and distorted shape as he fled <lb n="c58-0034__main__12"/> with more than mortal speed.<milestone xmlns:mith="http://mith.umd.edu/sc/ns1#" unit="tei:p"/> 
         <lb n="c58-0034__main__13"/> I pursued him; and for many months this <lb n="c58-0034__main__14"/> has been my task. Guided by a slight clue I follow<zone eID="c58-0034__main"/>
