         <add place="superlinear" sID="c58-0035__main__d6e2801"/>in a vessel <add eID="c58-0035__main__d6e2801"/>bound for the black sea and took my passage in <lb n="c58-0035__main__5"/> the same ship but he escaped I know not how;<milestone xmlns:mith="http://mith.umd.edu/sc/ns1#" unit="tei:p"/> 
