         <del rend="strikethrough" sID="c58-0035__main__d6e2867"/>to you<del eID="c58-0035__main__d6e2867"/> 
         <lb n="c58-0035__main__15"/> and agony unknown; how can you <del rend="strikethrough" sID="c58-0035__main__d6e2872"/>de<del eID="c58-0035__main__d6e2872"/> understand what <lb n="c58-0035__main__16"/> I have felt and still feel. Cold, want and fatigue were <lb n="c58-0035__main__17"/> the least pains which I was destined to endure; I was <lb n="c58-0035__main__18"/> cursed by some devil <mod sID="c58-0035__main__d6e2882"/>
